/**
 * Text Contrast Fixes
 * This file contains comprehensive fixes for text contrast issues across the site
 * to meet WCAG AA standards (minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio for normal text)
 */

/* ===== GENERAL TEXT CONTRAST FIXES ===== */

